    "lyrics": {
      "text": "The sol-diers___ stand--ing__ guard__ at__ Thy__ tomb,__ O__ my__ Sav--iour, be-came__ as__ dead__ on__ see--ing the__ light--ning-like An----gel____ who preached to__ the___ wom-en__ of_____ Thine a-ris----ing,__ O___ Ho--ly___ Lord.____ Thee we glo--ri--fy,____ Who_____ hast a-bol----ished__ cor---rup----tion; Thee__ do___ we__ a---dore,_____ Who from the grave____ hast__ a---ris----en and Who____ a-lone__ art_____ our____ God."
